# Determinants of NPAs in Indian Banks
**Tool:** R (Panel Data Analysis)
**Period:** 2014–2023 | 6 Banks | 10 Years

### Study Statement
Panel econometric analysis to identify key determinants of 
Non-Performing Assets (NPAs) in Indian Banks over 2014–2023.

### Methodology
- Pooled OLS
- Fixed Effects Model
- Random Effects Model
- Hausman Test for model selection
- Diagnostic tests and robust standard error correction

### Key Findings
- ROA, credit growth, inflation and GDP growth are key determinants of NPAs
